  ],
  "subject": [],
  "abstracts": [
    {
      "note": "",
      "abstract": "Establishes the \"clean fuel standard of 2026\"; provides such standard is intended to reduce greenhouse gas intensity from the on-road transportation sector, with further reductions to be implemented based upon advances in technology."
    }
